{"type": "article", "id": 23039, "title": "兼具用餐和工作的桌子", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-01T07:34:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 63, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110541pXR2GwlYxftyeEri.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一张兼具收纳和用餐功能的餐桌 carafe，用橡木制作。简洁优雅的外形让它具有餐桌的特征，桌子下面有简易的储藏空间和接线孔，让手机和电脑的电源线有了好去处。实现工作和生活的转化，是适合现代人的桌子。它有三种尺寸，<a href=\"http://charleswilsondesign.com/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021105381aXUy43Zup8fz6jk.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.65647922\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110539ZzxVGqYbIPksOWHF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49877751\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110539xfI4brG3H1Pl5maV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.18581907\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110539anw8063ZmgPBqW4E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.31662592\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110540p8DgdTVyuxCAbY36.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.32151589\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}